Anthrax, Italy
--------
Information received on [and dated] 4 Jun 2015 from Prof Dr Romano Marabelli, chief veterinary officer, secretary general, Ministry of Health, Rome, Italy

Summary:
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 22 May 2015
Date of confirmation of the event: 30 May 2015
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 30 Nov 2014
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: _Bacillus anthracis_
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks (1):
Outbreak 1 (anthrax): Dorgali, Nuoro, SARDEGNA
Date of start of the outbreak: 22 May 2015
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Affected animals:
Species / Susceptible / Cases Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
